5:["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-cream-50 min-h-screen font-sans selection:bg-brand-gold-500/30","children":[["$","section",null,{"className":"pt-28 pb-16 md:pt-36 md:pb-24 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 bg-brand-navy-800 relative overflow-hidden","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0 bg-hero-pattern opacity-10","aria-hidden":true}],["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-20 mix-blend-screen pointer-events-none","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"absolute top-0 right-0 w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-brand-gold-400 rounded-full blur-[150px] translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/3"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-20","children":["$","$L17",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-6 mb-8","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"w-16 h-[1px] gradient-accent-gold"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-eyebrow text-brand-gold-400","children":"About the Institute"}]]}],["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-h1 text-white mb-8","children":"Coaching education with a soul and a standard"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-h4 text-navy-100 font-normal leading-relaxed","children":"The International Coaching Institute exists because the world has enough people with advice and too few who can truly help someone change. We train coaches to do the harder, quieter work: to listen well, to see clearly, and to hold the space where real change happens. Our standards are demanding on purpose, because the people our graduates serve deserve nothing less."}]]}]}]]}],["$","section",null,{"className":"py-16 md:py-20 lg:py-24 bg-white border-t border-navy-100","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-[1440px] mx-auto w-full min-w-0 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-24","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"lg:col-span-4","children":["$","$L17",null,{"children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 mb-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"w-8 h-[1px] bg-brand-gold-500"}],["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-h2 text-brand-navy-900","children":"Our story"}]]}]}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"lg:col-span-8","children":["$","$L17",null,{"delay":0.1,"className":"prose prose-lg prose-brand max-w-3xl","children":["$","div",null,{"dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"<p>ICI was created by a group of experienced coaches and educators who kept seeing the same gap. Plenty of coaching qualifications taught technique, but few taught the depth, self-awareness and rigour that distinguish a coach people trust. We built the institute to close that gap, with one unusual decision at its heart: we would teach coaching one-to-one, the way coaching itself is done, rather than herding people through a classroom.</p><p>Today we train coaches entirely online, one-to-one, for clients all over the world. Our graduates want more than a certificate. They want the judgement, the craft and the standing to do this work well.</p>"}}]}]}]]}]}]}]]}]
